Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:51.30,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\fs30\frz15.145\c&HE2DCD2&\pos(310,228)}想要下雨的時候一起撐傘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:51.30,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\fs30\c&HADD0B2&\pos(606,268)}你喜歡我嗎
